                                ClickToFront

        This lets you bring a window to the front of the screen by holding
down the left Alt key and double clicking in the window - useful if you
have a lot of windows open and can't get to the window depth gadget easily.
To start ClickToFront, double click on its icon. To exit, double-click on
the icon again or use the Exchange program (see Utilities/Exchange) to kill
it. You can choose a different qualifier to the Alt key, or none at all,
using Tool Types.



